{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"看来你虽然比苗宣聪明得多，却还是不能算太聪明。","tone":"平静","chapter":61,"line_start":4,"line_end":4},{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"班察巴那故意公开宣布发动攻击，为的就是要我自己暴露出自己的行踪。","tone":"陈述","chapter":61,"line_start":10,"line_end":11},{"speaker":"char_sha_ping","speaker_name":"沙平","listener":"char_lv_san","text":"是的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":61,"line_start":16,"line_end":16},{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"所以我们绝不能这么样做，绝不能让他如愿。","tone":"认真","chapter":61,"line_start":12,"line_end":13},{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"可是我们也不能放弃这个机会，班察巴那是头老狐狸，我们要抓这条老狐狸，就不能放过这次机会。","tone":"认真","chapter":61,"line_start":18,"line_end":19},{"speaker":"char_sha_ping","speaker_name":"沙平","listener":"char_lv_san","text":"是的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":61,"line_start":22,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"所以我们一定要另外制造个陷阱，让他自己往下掉。","tone":"陈述","chapter":61,"line_start":24,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_sha_ping","speaker_name":"沙平","listener":"char_lv_san","text":"是的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":61,"line_start":26,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"班察巴那的属下，虽然全都是久经训练的战士，但是其中并没有真正的高手，只有一个人是例外。","tone":"沉声","chapter":61,"line_start":32,"line_end":33},{"speaker":"char_sha_ping","speaker_name":"沙平","listener":"char_lv_san","text":"谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":61,"line_start":36,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"小方。方伟！","tone":"陈述","chapter":61,"line_start":38,"line_end":38},{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"我本来一直低估了他。现在我才知道，这个人就像是个橡皮球一样，你不去动他，他好像连一点用都没有。如果你去打他一下，他说不定就会突然跳起来，你打得越用力，他就跳得越高，说不定一下子就会跳到你的头上来，要了你的命。","tone":"认真","chapter":61,"line_start":40,"line_end":43},{"speaker":"char_sha_ping","speaker_name":"沙平","listener":"char_lv_san","text":"是的。看起来他的确像是个这么样的人，所以别人才会称他为要命的小方。","tone":"陈述","chapter":61,"line_start":46,"line_end":47},{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"你知不知道他的行踪？","tone":"疑问","chapter":61,"line_start":50,"line_end":50},{"speaker":"char_sha_ping","speaker_name":"沙平","listener":"char_lv_san","text":"我知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":61,"line_start":52,"line_end":52},{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"这两天他在哪里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":61,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_sha_ping","speaker_name":"沙平","listener":"char_lv_san","text":"在拉萨。在拉萨的飞鹰楼，也就是以前鹰记商号接待客户的地方。","tone":"陈述","chapter":61,"line_start":56,"line_end":57},{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"你知不知道'三号'、'十三号'，和'二十三号'这几天在哪里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":61,"line_start":60,"line_end":61},{"speaker":"char_sha_ping","speaker_name":"沙平","listener":"char_lv_san","text":"我知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":61,"line_start":64,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"你能不能找得到他们？","tone":"疑问","chapter":61,"line_start":66,"line_end":66},{"speaker":"char_sha_ping","speaker_name":"沙平","listener":"char_lv_san","text":"能！六个时辰之内我就可以找到。","tone":"陈述","chapter":61,"line_start":68,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"那就好极了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":61,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_sha_ping","speaker_name":"沙平","listener":"char_lv_san","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":61,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"你知不知道我要他们去干什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":61,"line_start":76,"line_end":76},{"speaker":"char_sha_ping","speaker_name":"沙平","listener":"char_lv_san","text":"不知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":61,"line_start":78,"line_end":78},{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"去杀小方。我要他们去杀小方。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":61,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_lv_san","speaker_name":"吕三","listener":"char_sha_ping","text":"可是有一点你一定要记住，你绝不能让他们三个人同时出手。","tone":"严肃","chapter":61,"line_start":82,"line_end":83}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_lv_san","name":"吕三","alias":[],"identity":"庞大秘密组织的首领","faction":null,"role":"villain","archetype":"mastermind","rank":"登峰造极","one_line":"庞大秘密组织的首领，行事阴险狠毒，善于算计","personality":{"traits":["阴险","狠毒","算计","果断","多疑"],"speech_style":"沉稳威严","temperament":"冷酷深沉"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_sha_ping","type":"主仆","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"绝对控制"},{"target":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","type":"宿敌","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"相互博弈"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[61],"source_refs":[{"chapter":61,"line_start":2,"line_end":3,"text":"吕三笑得真愉快！"}]},{"id":"char_sha_ping","name":"沙平","alias":[],"identity":"吕三的心腹手下","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"吕三的心腹手下，绝对服从命令","personality":{"traits":["服从","沉默","高效","忠诚","冷酷"],"speech_style":"简洁","temperament":"沉稳内敛"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_lv_san","type":"主仆","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"绝对服从"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[61],"source_refs":[{"chapter":61,"line_start":6,"line_end":6,"text":"沙平完全同意。"}]},{"id":"char_ban_cha_ba_na","name":"班察巴那","alias":[],"identity":"与吕三对立的势力首领","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登峰造极","one_line":"与吕三对立的势力首领，被称为老狐狸","personality":{"traits":["狡猾","老练","精明","果断","勇猛"],"speech_style":null,"temperament":"老谋深算"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_lv_san","type":"宿敌","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"相互博弈"},{"target":"char_xiao_fang","type":"合作者","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"指挥与被指挥"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[61],"source_refs":[{"chapter":61,"line_start":10,"line_end":11,"text":"班察巴那故意公开宣布发动攻击"}]}